title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data are exported successfully. However, the actual result is that an exception occurs in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' method.
SR: To reproduce this bug: 1. Insert one table into a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell.
